subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: The Australian Open men’s final included psychological and physical struggles, with Stanislas Wawrinka playing a superb opening set and ultimately winning his battle with nerves to defeat an injured Rafael Nadal.
